               <p>SECOND COUNT, for feloniously nttering and publishing the same as true, well knowing the same to be false, forged, and counterfeited, with intention to defraud the said 
               <persName id="t18290409-320-person2957">
                  John 
                  Hipkiss
               <interp inst="t18290409-320-person2957" type="surname" value="Hipkiss"></interp>
